@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            h2:first-child {
                margin-top: 0;
            }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p>Thank you for using Agri-Energy Connect. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the types of information we collect, how we use it, and how we safeguard your privacy when you use our platform.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

        <p>When you register an account on Agri-Energy Connect, we collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and address. Additionally, we may collect information about your agricultural interests, preferences, and activities on our platform.</p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

        <p>We use the information we collect to provide you with a personalized experience on Agri-Energy Connect, including tailored product recommendations, educational resources, and community engagement opportunities. We may also use your information to communicate with you about platform updates, promotions, and relevant agricultural news.</p>

        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>

        <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as described in this Privacy Policy. We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our platform, conducting business activities, or servicing you, as long as those parties agree to keep this information confidential.</p>

        <h2>Security Measures</h2>

        <p>We are committed to ensuring the security of your personal information and have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.</p>

        <h2>Cookie Policy</h2>

        <p>Agri-Energy Connect may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze platform usage, and personalize content and advertisements. By using our platform, you consent to the use of cookies in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

        <p>We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and we encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>

        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at [info@agri-energyconnect.co.za].</p>

        <footer>Effective Date: [10/05/2024]</footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

